reviewText:
I'm not relly a platformer genre fan. I really dont like the idea of repeating the same action 10 times until I finnaly get the last jump right, BUT THIS GAME IS AWSOME.

-Nice art and voice acting;
-The plot is really simple but really fun to keep up with;
-It's not the type of platformer that will really challenge you;
-It's kind of relaxing and makes you happy : )

8,5/10
